    "Inspired by HNSW, Vamana and NGT proposed variants that support incremental graph building [31,158], but we classify them as ND-based per the ideas proposed in the original papers.",
    "HCNNG [102] was influenced by SPTAG [29] and adopted a DC approach for constructing the graph without adopting ND.",
    "ELPIS [11] also adopted a DC strategy but leveraged both II and ND.",
    "HVS [94] and LSHAPG [163] both propose new seed selection structures for HNSW, with the latter additionally adopting a new probabilistic rooting approach.",
